               <msContents>
                  <summary>Collection of letters of Emperor Menilek, Ras Tafari, Metropolitan Matewos, etc.  dated around 1917-1923. F. 1: Letter of warning from Emperor Menilek to people without work, directing them  go to a certain place for employment.  Dated 1902 EC. F. 3: A letter of Empress Zewditu expressing symphathy for the death of Qängazmač Bayana. Dated Maggabit 13, 1919 EC. <locus target="#4r"/>: Another copy of the letter in <locus target="#1r"/>.  This copy is written in Addis Ababa. <locus target="#5r"/>: A letter of condolence from Empress Zewditu on the death of Däjaz Balcha to the Addis Alem Church.</summary>
